  <scopecontent id="aspace_40fadd7ffbb91895acb8051616f82100">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes biographical material, correspondence, giving records and signatures of donors, personnel files, job search files, annual reports, project files, and conference files. Also, tape recordings.</p><p> Also, 61 color slides and a cassette, "There are Few Earthly Things More Beautiful Than a University," June 1974, produced by Visual Services.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <relatedmaterial id="aspace_34db2abd7ac6c9b9bc19aa1b10d02b05">
    <head>RELATED MATERIALS</head>
<p>Includes collections 4-3-883, 4-3-906, 4-3-1038, 4-3-1123, 4-3-1152, 4-3-1164, 4-3-1167, 4-3-622, 4-3-1336, 4-3-1350, 4-3-1454, 4-3-1493, and 4-3-913.</p>  </relatedmaterial>
